msgstr "此檔案來儲存環境的副本。"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:53
msgid ""
"Sometimes environment-saving fails because the environment can't be "
"pickled, and ``vars.pkl`` is empty. This is known to be a problem for Gym"
" Box2D environments in older versions of Gym, which can't be saved in "
"this manner."
msgstr ""
"有時環境儲存會失敗，因為環境無法被 pickle 序列化，此時 ``vars.pkl`` 會是空的。"
"這在舊版 Gym 的 Box2D 環境中是已知問題，這些環境無法以此方式儲存。"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:57
msgid ""
"As of 1/30/20, the save directory structure has changed slightly. "
"Previously, Tensorflow graphs were saved in the ``simple_save/`` folder; "
"this has been replaced with ``tf1_save/``."
msgstr ""
"自 2020 年 1 月 30 日起，儲存目錄結構略有變更。"
"以前，Tensorflow 計算圖儲存在 ``simple_save/`` 資料夾中；現已改為 ``tf1_save/``。"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:61
msgid ""
"The only file in here that you should ever have to use \"by hand\" is the"
" ``config.json`` file. Our agent testing utility will load things from "
"the ``tf1_save/`` or ``pyt_save/`` directory, and our plotter interprets "
"the contents of ``progress.txt``, and those are the correct tools for "
"interfacing with these outputs. But there is no tooling for "
"``config.json``---it's just there so that if you forget what "
"hyperparameters you ran an experiment with, you can double-check."
msgstr ""
"這裡唯一你可能需要「手動」使用的檔案是 ``config.json``。"
"我們的代理測試工具會從 ``tf1_save/`` 或 ``pyt_save/`` 目錄載入內容，"
"而繪圖工具會解讀 ``progress.txt`` 的內容，這些才是存取這些輸出的正確工具。"
"但 ``config.json`` 沒有專用工具——它存在的目的只是讓你在忘記實驗使用了哪些超參數時可以查閱。"

