#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:124
msgid "Loading and Running Trained Policies"
msgstr "載入和執行已訓練的策略"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:128
msgid "If Environment Saves Successfully"
msgstr "如果環境儲存成功"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:130
msgid ""
"For cases where the environment is successfully saved alongside the "
"agent, it's a cinch to watch the trained agent act in the environment "
"using:"
msgstr ""
"對於環境與代理一起成功儲存的情況，使用以下命令即可輕鬆觀看已訓練代理在環境中的表現："

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:138
msgid "There are a few flags for options:"
msgstr "有幾個選項旗標："

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:143
msgid ""
"*int*. Maximum length of test episode / trajectory / rollout. The default"
" of 0 means no maximum episode length---episodes only end when the agent "
"has reached a terminal state in the environment. (Note: setting L=0 will "
"not prevent Gym envs wrapped by TimeLimit wrappers from ending when they "
"reach their pre-set maximum episode length.)"
msgstr ""
"*int*。測試回合 (episode) / 軌跡 (trajectory) / 展開 (rollout) 的最大長度。"
"預設值 0 表示沒有最大回合長度——回合僅在代理到達環境的終止狀態時才結束。"
"（注意：設定 L=0 不會阻止被 TimeLimit 包裝器包裝的 Gym 環境在達到預設最大回合長度時結束。）"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:147
msgid "*int*. Number of test episodes to run the agent for."
msgstr "*int*。對代理執行的測試回合數。"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:151
msgid ""
"Do not render the test episodes to the screen. In this case, "
"``test_policy`` will only print the episode returns and lengths. (Use "
"case: the renderer slows down the testing process, and you just want to "
"get a fast sense of how the agent is performing, so you don't "
"particularly care to watch it.)"
msgstr ""
"不將測試回合渲染到螢幕上。在這種情況下，``test_policy`` 只會印出回合回報 (return) 和長度。"
"（使用情境：渲染器會減慢測試過程，而你只想快速了解代理的表現，不特別需要觀看。）"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:155
msgid ""
"*int*. This is an option for a special case which is not supported by "
"algorithms in this package as-shipped, but which they are easily modified"
" to do. Use case: Sometimes it's nice to watch trained agents from many "
"different points in training (eg watch at iteration 50, 100, 150, etc.). "
"The logger can do this---save snapshots of the agent from those different"
" points, so they can be run and watched later. In this case, you use this"
" flag to specify which iteration to run. But again: spinup algorithms by "
"default only save snapshots of the most recent agent, overwriting the old"
" snapshots."
msgstr ""
"*int*。這是一個特殊情況的選項，此套件出廠時不支援，但很容易修改以實現。"
"使用情境：有時候觀看訓練過程中不同時間點的代理表現很有用（例如觀看第 50、100、150 次迭代等）。"
"記錄器可以做到這點——儲存代理在不同時間點的快照，以便之後執行和觀看。"
"在這種情況下，你使用此旗標指定要執行的迭代次數。"
"但請注意：Spinning Up 演算法預設只儲存最新代理的快照，會覆蓋舊的快照。"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:157
msgid "The default value of this flag means \"use the latest snapshot.\""
msgstr "此旗標的預設值表示「使用最新的快照」。"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:159
msgid ""
"To modify an algo so it does produce multiple snapshots, find the "
"following line (which is present in all of the algorithms):"
msgstr "若要修改演算法使其產生多個快照，請找到以下程式碼行（所有演算法中都有）："

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:165
msgid "and tweak it to"
msgstr "並將其修改為"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:171
msgid ""
"Make sure to then also set ``save_freq`` to something reasonable (because"
" if it defaults to 1, for instance, you'll flood your output directory "
"with one ``save`` folder for each snapshot---which adds up fast)."
msgstr ""
"請確保同時將 ``save_freq`` 設定為合理的值"
"（因為如果保持預設值 1，你的輸出目錄會充滿每個快照一個的 ``save`` 資料夾——數量很快就會累積）。"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:176
msgid ""
"Another special case, which is only used for SAC. The Spinning Up SAC "
"implementation trains a stochastic policy, but is evaluated using the "
"deterministic *mean* of the action distribution. ``test_policy`` will "
"default to using the stochastic policy trained by SAC, but you should set"
" the deterministic flag to watch the deterministic mean policy (the "
"correct evaluation policy for SAC). This flag is not used for any other "
"algorithms."
msgstr ""
"另一個特殊情況，僅用於 SAC。Spinning Up 的 SAC 實作訓練的是隨機策略 (stochastic policy)，"
"但使用動作分佈的確定性*平均值*進行評估。``test_policy`` 預設使用 SAC 訓練的隨機策略，"
"但你應該設定 deterministic 旗標以觀看確定性平均策略"
"（SAC 的正確評估策略）。此旗標不用於其他任何演算法。"

