#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:213
msgid "Using Trained Value Functions"
msgstr "使用已訓練的價值函數"

#: ../../user/saving_and_loading.rst:215
msgid ""
"The ``test_policy.py`` tool doesn't help you look at trained value "
"functions, and if you want to use those, you will have to do some digging"
" by hand. For the PyTorch case, load the saved model file with "
"``torch.load`` and check the documentation for each algorithm to see what"
" modules the ActorCritic object has. For the Tensorflow case, load the "
"saved computation graph with the `restore_tf_graph`_ function, and check "
"the documentation for each algorithm to see what functions were saved."
msgstr ""
"``test_policy.py`` 工具無法幫助你查看已訓練的價值函數，如果你想使用它們，需要自行探索。"
"對於 PyTorch 的情況，使用 ``torch.load`` 載入已儲存的模型檔案，"
"並查閱各演算法的文件以了解 ActorCritic 物件包含哪些模組。"
"對於 Tensorflow 的情況，使用 `restore_tf_graph`_ 函式載入已儲存的計算圖，"
"並查閱各演算法的文件以了解哪些函式已被儲存。"
